# Ignore the SwiftPM package-root lockfile (this repo's root is a library
# package — its resolved file is a build artifact, not a committed lock).
# Do NOT use a bare `Package.resolved` here: that glob also swallows the app's
# Xcode workspace lockfile at
# App/GuessWho.xcodeproj/.../xcshareddata/swiftpm/Package.resolved, which MUST
# be committed — the app build has automatic dependency resolution disabled and
# requires that pinned file to be present and tracked.
/Package.resolved
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
AGENTS.md
.codex/
